text: <@U23602KDF> Hi Jennifer could we have it setup for portal 340557? Thanks!
Thanks Jeffrey we thrill with this update :smile:

Quick note for everyone <!here|@here>. HubDB will be officially released and announced at INBOUND next week. HubDB will require the Website Add-on ($300 version) and any portals with Website Starter will not receive it. Everyone in this channel that has requested access to HubDB for a specific portal now has it, and will be “grandfathered in". All portals going forward will need the Website add-on though.
If you have any questions, feel free to let <@U23602KDF> or myself know.
